    {
        "content": "<p>Lean doesn't allow for such types. Your best bet would be to define your <code>Free</code> mutually with your effect <code>I</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">mutual</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"kn\">inductive</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">FreeI</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">where</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Do</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">I</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">β</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">FreeI</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">FreeI</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Return</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">FreeI</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"kn\">inductive</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">I</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">where</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">FreeI</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">I</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">end</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
